# Listings

The Listings API allows consumers to view, add, modify, and delete listings.

## Listings Collection [/listings]

### List All Listings [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "url": "http://localhost:8000/listings/1/",
                "latitude": 49.278561162522,
                "longitude": -123.10757743748,
