### Create a New Listing [POST]

You may create a new listing using this action. It takes a JSON object containing the listing attributes. Make sure the `neighbourhood` field contains the name of an existing neighbourhood.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Token TOKEN

    + Body

            {
                "latitude": 49.266587366733,
                "longitude": -123.14911563962,
                "neighbourhood": "Kitsilano",
                "price": 3242,
                "date_listed": 1466523420,
                "bedrooms": 1,
                "bathrooms": 0,
                "description": "Beautiful Vancouver Townhouse",
                "listing_url": "https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/1233101?checkin=2016-09-01&checkout=2016-09-30&af=3483444",
                "listing_id": 253289601,
                "address": "W 6th Ave, Vancouver, BC V6J 1R7"
            }

